---
title: Housing Choice — Tenant Onboarding (Phase 1)
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor T as Tenant
    participant A as Housing Choice App
    participant S as Sam
    Note over T,S: The app owns the phone number. Every message flows between Tenant and Sam through the app (both directions).<br/>Notes marked [AUTO] are app automation. Sam's messages are manual comms (Phase 1).
    Note over S: Preferences are captured from feedback, not asked upfront<br/>(she's not their personal shopper)
    loop Until a listing fits
        S->>A: Send a specific listing for feedback
        A->>T: Deliver listing
        opt Tenant shares preferences
            T->>A: e.g., no stairs (walker), near MARTA,<br/>near kid's school, must fit a king bed
            Note over A: [MANUAL] Save preferences to tenant profile<br/>(remembered for future matches)
            A->>S: Relay preferences
        end
        S->>A: Find another match
        A-->>S: Next matching listing
    end
    Note over T,S: Hand off to Tours workflow (separate)